{"word":"G1553 - ἐκδημέω - ekdēméō - ek-day-meh'-o - Be absent","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκδημέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ekdēméō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ek-day-meh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Be absent</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - குடியிராதவனாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"1. to go abroad"},{"paragraph":"2. to be or live abroad"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G1218 - δῆμος - dēmos - day'-mos/1218\">G1218</a>; to <i>emigrate</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>vacate</i> or <i>quit:</i> - be absent.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1218/1218\">G1218</a>, <a href=\"#/G1553/1553\">G1553</a>, <a href=\"#/G1736/1736\">G1736</a>, <a href=\"#/G3927/3927\">G3927</a>"}]}